              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/.The Elastic Correction was Calculated",
                "Taking Into Account the Finite Size of the Beam and the",
                "Angular Distribution of Multiple Coulomb Scattering in",
                "The Passing Counters and in the Target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two Separate Targets were Used For the Measurements of",
                "The Total Reaction Cross Section on Carbon.Each Target",
                "Was Self-Supporting Natural Carbon of 99% Purity.One",
                "Target,Having an Areal Density of 0.015 G/Cm**2,was",
                "Used For Measurements at 17.41 and 19.46 MeV.The Other",
                "Target,Having an Areal Density of 0.00449 G/Cm**2,was",
                "Used For All Other Measurements.",
                "The Targets were Examined For Roughness and",
                "Irregularities,and Small Corrections were Made If",
                "Necessary.",
                "With Each Target,a Thin (0.00247 G/CM**2) Nickel Foil",
                "Was Placed in Front of the Carbon."
              ]
            }
          ],
