              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Four Targets of Ca-40 were Used For the Total Reaction",
                "Measurements.The Thickness was Chosen So That the",
                "Average Energy Loss in the Target was Between 235 and",
                " 325 KeV.The Targets were Made from Foils.They",
                "Contained 99.97% Ca-40.The Oxygen Present in the Foils",
                "Was Estimated to be Less Than 1% of the Weight of the",
                "Foils.",
                "Each Targets was Examined For Irregularities and",
                "Appropriate Corrections were Made.The Areal Densities",
                "Of the Four Targets were 10.0,10.3,12.2 and 14.1 Mg/",
                "Cm**2."
              ]
            }
